The '''cave goblin guards''' guard the [[Dorgeshuun Mines]]. They can be seen patrolling the mines with their [[Bone spear|boney spears]] or [[Bone club|clubs]]. They protect the [[cave goblin miner]]s, and will command, ''"Stop that!"'', and begin to attack you if you are spotted assaulting a miner.

